FR940822-2-00166 FR940822-2-00061 State Justice Institute_Scholarship Application; Concurrence (Form S2) I, Name of Chief Justice (or Chief Justice's Designee) have reviewed the application for a scholarship to attend the program entitled prepared by Name of Applicant and concur in its submission to the State Justice Institute. The applicant's participation in the program would benefit the State; the applicant's absence to attend the program would not present an undue hardship to the court; and receipt of a scholarship would not diminish the amount of funds made available by the State for judicial education. Signature Name Title Date
